    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Árpád Rusz</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:182px;\"><a href=\"http://ruszchessstudies.blogspot.com/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e0/ArpadRusz.jpg/180px-ArpadRusz.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"241\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/e/e0/ArpadRusz.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ArpadRusz.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Árpád Rusz <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Árpád Rusz</b>,<br />\na Romanian chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/Category:Chess_Composer\" title=\"Category:Chess Composer\">chess endgame study composer</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> . He contributed along with <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> on <i>Position Criticality</i> in Chess Endgames at the <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_13\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 13\">Advances in Computer Games 13</a> conference in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tilburg\">Tilburg</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> , demonstrating the implementation of their algorithm to help analyze uniqueness in endgame positions objectively with a chess variant called <a href=\"/index.php?title=Starchess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Starchess (page does not exist)\">Starchess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> , invented by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%A1szl%C3%B3_Polg%C3%A1r\">László Polgár</a> in 2002, which has a star-shaped board of 37 <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hexagon\">hexagons</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Postings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Postings</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy McCrossan Haworth</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-31866-5_21\">Position Criticality in Chess Endgames</a></i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_13\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 13\">Advances in Computer Games 13</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Postings\">Postings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Postings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=2404\">The RNN/RB endgame</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arpad Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, July 05, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chessproblem.net/viewtopic.php?f=12&amp;t=224#p441\">Re: \"Wrong-footed\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arpad Rusz</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chessproblem.net/index.php\">ChessProblem.net</a>, March 25, 2008</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=350127&amp;t=34433\">Analysing with an engine - an idea</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 21, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=5555\">Polgar Superstar Chess (Starchess)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arpad Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, December 13, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=5557\">EGTB studies</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arpad Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, December 13, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=383374&amp;t=37243\">Test position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=410026&amp;t=39332\">Re: max amount of moves from a position?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=435662&amp;t=41276\">A Knight endgame</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 01, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44544\">BPP against NP</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 22, 2012</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57949\">A possible new pawn structure evaluation term?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59273\">My troubles with MultiPV and Syzygy in Stockfish 7</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ruszchessstudies.blogspot.com/2016/11/corresponding-squares-1.html\">Corresponding Squares 1</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ruszchessstudies.blogspot.com/\">Chess Endgame Study Composition</a>, November 24, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Corresponding_Squares\" title=\"Corresponding Squares\">Corresponding Squares</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ruszchessstudies.blogspot.com/\">Chess Endgame Study Composition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=1210548\">Rusz, Arpad FIDE Chess Profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.365chess.com/players/Arpad_Rusz\">Arpad Rusz chess games - 365Chess.com</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ruszchessstudies.blogspot.com/\">Chess Endgame Study Composition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.365chess.com/players/Arpad_Rusz\">Arpad Rusz chess games - 365Chess.com</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.magyarsakkszerzok.com/Study_Award_MSV_2006.pdf\">Informal Tourney \"Magyar Sakkvilag – 2006\" The award and the judgement report A/ General category B/ Database category</a> (pdf)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy McCrossan Haworth</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Árpád Rusz</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Position Criticality in Chess Endgames</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_13\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 13\">Advances in Computer Games 13</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.polgarstarchess.com/Home/ENHome.html\">Polgar Starchess</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://polgarstarchess.blogspot.com/\">Polgar Superstar Chess (Starchess)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301103837\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 115/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 242/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4615-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301103837 and revision id 8410\n -->\n"
